bamtools
------------------------------------------
BamTools provides both a programmer's API and an end-user's toolkit for
handling BAM files.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.9.0-3
  libbamtools-devel-2.4.1-1bl2
  libbamtools2.4.1-2.4.1-1bl2
  libgcc1-6.4.0-1
  libjsoncpp19-1.8.3-1bl1
  libstdc++6-6.4.0-1
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1
  zlib0-1.2.11-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.28-3
  cmake-3.6.2-1
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-6.4.0-1
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/pezmaster31/bamtools

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/pezmaster31/bamtools/archive/v2.4.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bamtools-2.4.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bamtools-2.4.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bamtools-2.4.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bamtools-2.4.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbamtools2.4.1-2.4.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbamtools-devel-2.4.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(bamtools)
  /usr/bin/bamtools
  /usr/bin/bamtools-2.4.1.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/bamtools.README
  /usr/share/doc/bamtools/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/bamtools/README

(libbamtools2.4.1)
  /usr/bin/cygbamtools-2.4.1.dll

(libbamtools-devel)
  /usr/include/bamtools/api/BamAlgorithms.h
